johar.interfaceinterpreter.star
Class CommandController

java.lang.Object
  johar.interfaceinterpreter.star.CommandController
All Implemented Interfaces:
CommandControllerBase
public class CommandController
extends java.lang.Object
implements CommandControllerBase

The Command Controller class interacts with the Widgets; It performs any action required by the user, while handling all events generated by the Widgets; It interacts with the Gem via GemSetting and the Idf to serve requests raised from the Widgets.
